e><br />\n四萬幾買每年要廿萬玩<br />\n好金</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係，條台仔話部車係好玩，但d件真係唔耐用，加上舊左乜都到期，郁下就番廠，最麻煩係一般車房無件整唔到，就算番原廠都要訂件訂好耐，又貴又要等。<br />\n<br />\n我都好想買，一個月平均洗多兩皮幾三皮保養，玩唔起 :("},{"pid":"361980a6985554688d949ed420a670d52937325d","tid":128551,"uid":31990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T02:56:02.000Z","msg":"但佢把聲真係好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68dca6d38eabcd85d42524f56ede38e821b9661c","tid":128551,"uid":61563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T03:33:19.000Z","msg":"差啲中招 好彩有上黎問 唔該各位師兄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"163920c4db6a37e1ffe18e56ddcd5bb505375aef","tid":128551,"uid":61563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T03:41:16.000Z","msg":"搭單問有冇其他歐洲跑可以諗 好想圓夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68765b8d18d519721bd423dd1847c5ef13b2e98d","tid":128551,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T03:42:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>搭單問有冇其他歐洲跑可以諗 好想圓夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n雷諾鋼炮仔，再唔係VW Sir樂高，寶馬M，Benz CLA"},{"pid":"407cc9d30b255d995ecfe24caa3dbd26088ad8a8","tid":128551,"uid":51121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T03:46:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>搭單問有冇其他歐洲跑可以諗 好想圓夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無錢玩一手, 其實都無錢玩二手.<br />\n<br />\n難搵車房整, 原廠咩都貴, 保養要做足唔係仲貴. 油費又貴, 真係一個月皮費起碼一萬."},{"pid":"83f39e3cbcf61eb81edeb466ab88337d580a82d9","tid":128551,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T03:47:34.000Z","msg":"470 K  下話 ? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3613f085cc9e00316d721945dd8484799deab647","tid":128551,"uid":30006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T03:49:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote